citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:00a-11:30a
on 03-DEC-19.
ACI Bartels arrived at the location, called all the numbers on file, and honked the horn of the government vehicle.
Due to a gated entrance ACI Bartels was not able to knock on the main door, or ring a doorbell.
